<p style="text-align: justify;">Currently he is playing for Cerezo Osaka, a local club of OsakaÂ  with jersey number 9.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">1.87m tall Sugimoto is right footed and currently plays Japanese league. The talented Sugimoto has scored five times in a single game against Cambodia national team under 15 playing for Japanese national team under 15 in AFC under 16 championship qualifications. The game was held on Jakarta capital city of Indonesia the final score of the game was 7-0 in which combodian failed to score against Japan.</p>
